# Portfolio Template 1

A responsive and modern personal portfolio template built using only HTML and CSS. This template is perfect for showcasing your projects, skills, and personal information.

##  Features

- Clean, minimalist design
- Mobile-first approach
- Sections for About, Projects, Contact, 
- Custom styles using pure CSS (no frameworks)

##  Files

- `portfolio.html` – The main HTML file for the portfolio layout
- `style.css` – The stylesheet for styling the portfolio

##  Preview

Open `portfolio.html` in your browser to see the portfolio in action.

##  Usage

1. Clone or download the repo
2. Open `portfolio.html` in a web browser
3. Customize the content and style as needed

```bash
git clone https://github.com/faresabe/portfolio_template-1.git
cd portfolio_template-1
